      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty daily driver. It's been such a fantastic car for me\u2014super dependable and still looks really sharp! I've taken great care of it, so it runs smoothly and is totally ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a solid, well-loved ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
