    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of light use that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is firm and free of any tears or significant staining, and all power features, including the climate control and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection just completed. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an immediate replacement. We have kept a detailed log of all maintenance performed during our ownership, which will be handed over to the new owner. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 32500.0,
